{"tid":2323432,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】泫雅超性感禮服上陣險走光　太吸睛連粉絲都睇唔過眼？","createTime":"2020-12-13T07:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T11:51:51.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e7e816d4c185ef678bf834882c0e56f1b87505c9","tid":2323432,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T07:30:46.000Z","msg":"有「性感小野馬」之稱的韓國歌手泫雅擁姣好身材這件事可謂街知巷聞，而她亦毫不吝嗇展示，不時在個人IG派福利。周六（12日）泫雅上載了一系列在髮型屋拍攝的照片，旁邊有髮型師正為她整理，不過穿着超性感白色禮裙的她似乎一刻也停不下來，擺着各種姿勢望向鏡頭，豐滿的上圍及白滑長腿都相當吸睛，性感到有走光的危機，不禁令人捏一把冷汗！粉絲們除了連連大讚美麗，還擔心說：「姐姐，穿得溫暖一點吧！」"},{"pid":"353b71bb193c7f31d6ef7b47cad5e3b4d2e95acd","tid":2323432,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T07:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201212/414544652729847808461509.jpeg/mHFNeP0gpXYtj7O2DLkUyc1OjezFUwISJS3UlCUt1JQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201212%2F414544652729847808461509.jpeg%2FmHFNeP0gpXYtj7O2DLkUyc1OjezFUwISJS3UlCUt1JQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1be157da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201212/414544654558695424167592.jpeg/MQQ6uJZIfkZi6auHSUW0Jthb5ytEdw7D24NT_duDU_0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201212%2F414544654558695424167592.jpeg%2FMQQ6uJZIfkZi6auHSUW0Jthb5ytEdw7D24NT_duDU_0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c2852a9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201212/414544656450457600135748.jpeg/XSocd53s4AGkbg_1D6jI22Y8vC6KdAtzr0ECJK9BAiQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201212%2F414544656450457600135748.jpeg%2FXSocd53s4AGkbg_1D6jI22Y8vC6KdAtzr0ECJK9BAiQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=baed07ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d03cbf05764ab3f556bc4977c4b48cfa2301b2b7","tid":2323432,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"